HEADWORD: Impassioned
<hw>Im*pas"sioned</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>p. p. & a.</pos> <def>Actuated
or characterized by passion or zeal; showing warmth of feeling; ardent;
animated; excited; <as>as, an <ex>impassioned</ex> orator or
discourse</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impassive</ent>⟦br⟧
